208
00:10:12,129 --> 00:10:13,232
{\pos(192,205)}de ce cirque.

209
00:10:13,441 --> 00:10:14,864
{\pos(192,205)}À cause de ma maladie ?

210
00:10:15,342 --> 00:10:18,993
{\pos(192,205)}Votre dernière rencontre s'est soldée
